blog.title: I Know I Never Think Before I Jump - T.S
blog.description: I'm Alicia, from Rhode Island but living in PA. I’m just trying to be the kind of person Taylor would be proud of. Taylor followed me on December 8th, 2014 and invited me to her house in Westerly, RI on 10/18/17 to hear reputation in its entirety, weeks before its release. She held my hands so tight and told me she loved seeing my bright sunshiny face all the time. I died. The end.
